  "author": "Decent",
  "notes": "This profile is optimized for the 7g Decent Basket.  You should weigh 7g of beans and dose them into the center mini-basket at the bottom.  You'll need a small 36mm tamper.  The flow rate is slowed down to prevent disturbing the puck.  A lower pressure is used to compensate for the lower puck integrity.  Final shot weight should be 18 to 28 grams.",
